      "published": "27 Feb 2026, 18:12",
      "summary": "“VOY A LLeVARTE PA PR“ (“I'm Going to Take You to PR“) is a song by Puerto Rican rapper Bad Bunny. It was released on January 5, 2025, with his sixth solo studio album, DeBÍ TiRAR MáS FOToS.\n\nThe visualizer for \"Voy a Llevarte Pa' PR\" narrates the war after the war (1898-1899).\n\nBad Bunny performed this song at his Super Bowl halftime show. <a href=\"http://www.last.fm/music/Bad+Bunny/_/VOY+A+LLeVARTE+PA+PR\">Read more on Last.fm</a>.",
